<h3 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h3>
<p>We now integrate this to find the ball's position.</p>
<div class="displaymath process-math" data-contains-math-knowls="">
\begin{align*}
\dfdx{y}{t}\amp=-9.8t+19.6\\
\dx{y}\amp=\left(-9.8t+19.6\right)\dx{t}\\
\int\dx{y}\amp=-\int\left(9.8t+19.6\right)\dx{t}\\
y\amp=-9.8\left(\frac{t^2}{2}\right)+19.6t+c
\end{align*}
</div>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-3.html#p-35" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
